THIS APPLICATION
================================================================================

Mahikeng Civic Safety PWA is a civic infrastructure reporting and community
safety platform built for the residents of Mahikeng. It is not open-source
software. The source code is made available for transparency and auditability,
but all modification and redistribution rights are reserved by the author.

